title: McKayla Maroney Shared A Few Very Nice Reminders Why She’ll Always Be Our Favorite Gymnast
text:
The last time we discussed out favorite gymnast McKayla Maroney I was questioning the fact that she looked a little, uh, “different.” 
I don’t really know why she looked different, she just did. 
Late last night McKayla shared some pics and a video to her Twitter which showed that us much as we appreciated seeing Aly Raisman in the SI Swimsuit Issue , and we certainly did, they may have missed the boat with McKayla because putting her in that issue would be straight money.
Here’s proof, as provided by her…
mood pic.twitter.com/462hxhN59N 
— McKayla Maroney (@McKaylaMaroney) March 20, 2017 

McKayla Maroney



McKayla Maroney, Twitter

She also shared this photo as well…
pic.twitter.com/oSUDJgPNum 
— McKayla Maroney (@McKaylaMaroney) March 20, 2017 

Yo, Sports Illustrated , if you think Danica Patrick did well back in the day, take a look right here. Just sayin’. She’s our favorite gymnast for a reason, folks.

— McKayla Maroney (@McKaylaMaroney) March 8, 2017
